  "description": "macroKnot=0.9 sits almost entirely in the Solomon topology with only a sliver of Trefoil influence from the wrap-around interpolation. The coupling matrix is almost entirely the two-ring Solomon architecture — but 10% of the Trefoil's directed three-strand ring persists as an asymmetric ghost, injecting directional energy into the Solomon pairs. S&H LFO on braid depth at 2.4 Hz: the topology suddenly lunges between depths, a stochastic wrenching of the coupling coefficients. Square strands add hard edge. This is what a knot sounds like when it cannot decide whether to untie itself.",
